column5: Are they still in business? I haven't seen any posts or changes on their web page since 2007. Thanks!

It's my understanding that the camp went out of business several years ago. The fellow who ran it (called himself "Agate" on WC) also teamed up to run another Canadian fishing web site. He had some very interesting posts on both sites, I was sorry to see it end. I spent some time at the camp (different owner)back in the early '70's - an adventurous part of the north woods. Bill
Yes, they are now out of business. This was on my short list a couple of years ago.
